Class EDIF300BaseVisitor<Result>

This class provides an empty implementation of IEDIF300Visitor<Result>, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.

Inheritance
System.Object
EDIF300BaseVisitor<Result>
Implements
IEDIF300Visitor<Result>
IParseTreeVisitor<Result>
Namespace: GCore.Antlr.Grammers.Edif300
Assembly: Edif300.dll
Syntax
public class EDIF300BaseVisitor<Result> : AbstractParseTreeVisitor<Result>, IEDIF300Visitor<Result>, IParseTreeVisitor<Result>

Name Description
Result

The return type of the visit operation.
